{"tid":1996023,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"聽日出街嘅人，提醒你少少野","createTime":"2020-04-30T16:34:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-09T17:07:56.000Z","uid":296607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e6babee30e599ac62715ae9e05475ac0938adc0b","tid":1996023,"uid":296607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:34:53.000Z","msg":"第一，<span style=\"color: gold;\">切勿輕敵</span>。<br />\n班黑警操左咁耐，就係等聽日咬曬你地，一次過打沉街頭抗爭。所以，聽日出街前，一定要諗好<span style=\"color: red;\">逃生路線</span>，眼看八方。如果齋企唔知有咩好做嘅話，走啦，去食黃店就得啦。<span style=\"color: red;\">無計劃只有一個下埸，等比狗咬。</span><br />\n<br />\n第二，<span style=\"color: gold;\">保護自己</span>。<br />\nBlackbloc又好乜都好，<span style=\"color: red;\">耳仔、輪廓</span>都唔可以比班狗認到，行完一段路就睇記得清楚有無CCTV。 <span style=\"color: red;\">帶多套衫褲鞋襪換</span>。<br />\n<br />\n第三，<span style=\"color: gold;\">偽勇武退場</span>，偽勇嘅存在只會令識衝嘅手足更危險，希望你地先退下火線，諗清楚聽日要做啲咩，破到心理關口，計劃好先出黎行街。<br />\n<br />\n第四，<span style=\"color: gold;\">切勿屌狗</span>，發生過無數次，無意義地屌狗導致被狗咬，而被咬嘅都唔係屌狗嘅你地，而係企喺最前嘅手足。<br />\n<br />\n最後一個提醒，近日粉嶺PTU總部經常訓練，就算夜晚12點都有槍聲，唔係手槍砰、砰、砰，而係噠噠噠噠噠，一連串連射。各位一切小心<br />\n<br />\n利申<br />\n其實我只係想出街食飯，希望班狗咪撚搞鳩我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f08d8e06f36940607626d513599934d77699cfb2","tid":1996023,"uid":296607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:38:07.000Z","msg":"黃金週大家上街食飯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e8446e31b9c2a6a0ad9e2e5b2f2b1efde90b493","tid":1996023,"uid":296607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:51:03.000Z","msg":"知道啦樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71f1b4c1dc0bc1a35aaea40e93f66f6da1b23fbc","tid":1996023,"uid":14941,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T17:28:46.000Z","msg":"tg收到風聽日重點係迫出tg"},{"pid":"a32ff6e139a179347226781f8de8b3252f867542","tid":1996023,"uid":252155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7e8446e31b9c2a6a0ad9e2e5b2f2b1efde90b493","tid":1996023,"uid":296607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T16:51:03.000Z","msg":"知道啦樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T17:31:01.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"88a56129a2fd4930b5849ec3faeeb67dbf6ee729","tid":1996023,"uid":337119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-30T17:36:41.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"8c4cf752552ff0eeb4b8095c4aeff4bbbda88ae0","tid":1996023,"uid":296607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T17:07:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65f433a1f2901c7849b852d7e080387fe9c2a3c","tid":1996023,"uid":296607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-09T17:07:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}